{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSRadioItem","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV","role":"symbol","platforms":[{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false}],"roleHeading":"Structure"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(_:isOn:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(_:tableName:bundle:isOn:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)"]},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"reversed","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The radio indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and optional texts and a custom radio trait."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection)","","    \/\/ Localizable from bundle can also be used","    OUDSRadioItem(LocalizedStringKey(\"option_label\"), bundle: Bundle.module, isOn: $selection)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, extraLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, extraLabel: \"The Beatles\", description: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, a description, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  description: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  isError: true,","                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $selection)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $selection, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $selection, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Cocorico !\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version","style":"note"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioIt